---
import Container from "./Container.astro";

---
<div id="full" class="mx-auto">
    <Container>
        <div>
            <div class="lg:w-3/4 mx-auto">
                <div class="my-8 flex flex-row place-content-start">
                    <div>
                        <img
                        src="/images/icons/help.png"
                        class="w-12 fill-white"
                        width="512"
                        height="512"
                        alt="clasped hands illustration"
                        />
                    </div>
                    <div><h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-4xl pl-2">Full Coaching</h2></div>
                </div>
                
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">With Full Coaching, you get a more hands-on approach tailored (and priced) for your needs.
                    We'll draft a custom Statement of Work (SOW) to cover the topics and processes you care about. 
                    I'll get to know your project and organization in detail and provide sessions and homework to get you where you want to be.
                </p>

                <p class="pt-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Sessions and deliverables in this Full Coaching package can include:</p>
            </div>
            <div
            class="space-y-6 justify-between text-gray-600 md:flex flex-row md:gap-6 md:space-y-0 lg:gap-12 lg:items-center lg:w-3/4 mx-auto"
            >
                <div class="md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/2">
                    <div
                        class="divide-y space-y-4 divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800"
                    >
                        <div class="mt-8 pb-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300"
                                >
                                    Key Players
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or define a list of key stakeholders and champions,
                                    as well as strategies for getting--and keeping--their buy-in.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-300"
                                >
                                    Proof of Concept
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or develop a Proof of Concept (POC) or Minimal Viable Product (MVP) to showcase what the documentation site can do.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-fuchsia-600 dark:text-fuchsia-300"
                                >
                                    Champions Cultivation
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or define a plan for identifying, cultivating, and rewarding knowledge champions and contributors.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/2">
                    <div
                        class="divide-y space-y-4 divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800"
                    >
                        <div class="mt-8 pb-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-300"
                                >
                                    Onboarding
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or define onboarding exercises, communication, or content for your end-users.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-orange-600 dark:text-orange-300"
                                >
                                    Communications Plan
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or create a list of communications, timeline, and rough content to announce the documentation,
                                    share progress, and maintain momentum.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-4 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
                            <div class="w-5/6">
                                <h3
                                    class="font-semibold text-lg text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-300"
                                >
                                    Launch Plan
                                </h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                                    We'll discuss and/or draft a comprehensive plan tying the other deliverables together.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-3/4 mx-auto">
                <h3 class="my-8 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Cost: <span class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Varies based on deliverables, length of engagement, etc.</span></h3>
            </div>
        <div>
    </Container>
</div>